window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Perron Manor - a place evil calls home.</b></p> <p>Sisters Sarah and Chloe inherit a house they could never have previously dreamed of owning. It seems too good to be true. Shortly after they move in, however, the siblings start to notice strange things: horrible smells, sudden drops in temperature as well as unexplainable sounds and feelings of being watched. All of that is compounded when they find a study upstairs, filled with occult items and a strange book written in Latin.</p> <p>Their experiences grow more frequent and more terrifying, building toward a heart-stopping climax when the sisters come face to face with the evil behind Perron Manor. Will they survive and save their very souls?</p>"; 
